              Lowboy Trailers
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              A <strong>lowboy trailer</strong> is a heavy-duty flatbed with an ultra-low deck height, ideal for transporting oversized, tall, or bulky equipment. With load capacities ranging from <strong>25 to 35 tons</strong>, it’s the perfect solution for hauling <strong>construction machinery</strong>, <strong>agricultural equipment</strong>, and other <strong>heavy loads</strong> that exceed standard height limits.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="relative h-full" data-aos="fade-left">
           <img src="/img/lowboy.webp" width="1000" height="461" class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl w-full object-cover" alt="heavy haul shipping lowboy"/>
        </div>
